content:
(9/n) So what are the various presentations in #bipolardisorder ?
1. A single #manic episode
2. #mania , hypomania, #depression , mixed state in separate episodes in various permutations & combinations.
3. Recurrent #mania 

A recurrent #depression only episodes is not ❌
👇🏽

rawContent:
(8/n) For a #bipolardisorder to be diagnosed, the above episodes (#mania , #depression & #mixed) need to happen in various timespans of a person’s life in varying intensities, durations & proportions. 
These episodes are separated by periods of full/ apparent remission. 👇🏽

rawContent:
(7/n) Often, in an index episode of #bipolardisorder , a mixture of both #depression & #mania can be co-existing in varying proportions for a span of time (months?).

This is a Mixed episode, which also jeopardises individual thinking, feeling, decision making & functioning. 👇🏽
